text: Victor Öhman (born July 1, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Sparta Warriors of the GET-ligaen (GET). Öhman made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Modo Hockey during the 2012–13 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:IF Björklöven players Category:Modo Hockey players Category:IK Oskarshamn players Category:Sparta Warriors players Category:Västerviks IK players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
